text: Snakehead is a 2021 American crime drama action-thriller movie directed by Evan Jackson Leong. The movie stars Shuya Chang, Jade Wu, and Sung Kang. It happens around a Chinese immigrant who becomes stuck in an international crime ring of human smuggling while trying to create a better life for her family. ==References== Category:2021 action movies Category:2021 drama movies Category:2021 thriller movies Category:2020s American action movies Category:2020s American drama movies Category:2020s English-language movies Category:American thriller movies
